chat_history.content:
Here is a list of the Summer Olympic Games held between the years 2000 and 2020:

1. 2000 Summer Olympics - Hosted in Sydney, Australia
2. 2004 Summer Olympics - Athens, Greece
3. 2008 Summer Olympics - Beijing, China
4. 2012 Summer Olympics - London, United Kingdom
5. 2016 Summer Olympics - Rio de Janeiro, Brazil
6. 2020 Summer Olympics - Tokyo, Japan

Would you like to know more about any of these Olympic Games?
chat_history.name: delegate

chat_history.content:
Certainly! Here are the main stadiums used for the opening and closing ceremonies of the Olympic Games in the past decade:

2010 Winter Olympics (Vancouver, Canada): BC Place Stadium

2012 Summer Olympics (London, United Kingdom): Olympic Stadium

2014 Winter Olympics (Sochi, Russia): Fisht Olympic Stadium

2016 Summer Olympics (Rio de Janeiro, Brazil): Maracanã Stadium

2018 Winter Olympics (Pyeongchang, South Korea): Pyeongchang Olympic Stadium

Would you like to know more about any of these stadiums or the Olympic Games themselves? I can provide additional information if needed.
chat_history.name: delegate

chat_history.content:
Great! Here is a list of the host cities and the main stadiums used for the Summer Olympic Games between 2000 and 2020:

2000 Summer Olympics, Sydney, Australia: Stadium Australia

2004 Summer Olympics, Athens, Greece: Athens Olympic Stadium

2008 Summer Olympics, Beijing, China: Beijing National Stadium (also known as the Bird's Nest)

2012 Summer Olympics, London, United Kingdom: Olympic Stadium

2016 Summer Olympics, Rio de Janeiro, Brazil: Maracanã Stadium

2020 Summer Olympics, Tokyo, Japan: Japan National Stadium

Let me know if you'd like to know more about any of these stadiums or the Olympic Games in general!
